column5: Got an email sale flyer from Cabellas this morning and saw this deal on a GPS and thought fer sure someone may be interested in it.  http://www.cabelas.com/cabelas/en/template...p;cmCat=catrtel
It is on backorder...do we still get the sale price when they come in? Garmin's map supplier, MAPTEQ was bought out by rival GPS company Tom Tom. Lots of Garmin sales soon, I would suspect.
oh wow.. super deal.. too bad i don't need a street pilot
